snippet.title: Top 3 Programming Languages to Learn in 2019
snippet.description:
Top 3 Programming Languages to Learn in 2019

In this video I share my suggestions for the top 3 programming languages that I think you should learn in 2019.
My recommendations are mostly based on the programming languages that are in the highest demand right now. 
Hope you enjoy it and get something out of it!
